

Are You encountering a Redirect to xampp/dashboard every vhost set for a laravel project.

here is the solution
====================

The issue mainly because of the ssl not setup for the project named host

solution video link : 
<a href="">https://ourcodeworld.com/articles/read/198/enabling-ssl-https-protocol-with-xampp-in-a-local-php-project</a>

Eg : vhost sample

<VirtualHost 127.0.0.2:80>
	DocumentRoot "C:/xampp/htdocs/laravel-project/public"
	DirectoryIndex index.php
	ServerName laravel.local
	<Directory "C:/xampp/htdocs/laravel-project/public">
		Options All
		AllowOverride All
		Require all granted
	</Directory>
</VirtualHost>

<VirtualHost 127.0.0.2:443>
	DocumentRoot "C:/xampp/htdocs/laravel-project/public"
	DirectoryIndex index.php
	SSLEngine on
	SSLCertificateFile "conf/ssl.crt/server.crt"
	SSLCertificateKeyFile "conf/ssl.key/server.key"

	ServerName laravel.local
	<Directory "C:/xampp/htdocs/laravel-project/public">
		Options All
		AllowOverride All
		Require all granted
	</Directory>
</VirtualHost>
